{"tid":1063884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李克強談改革效率︰一竿子插到底，插到市場主體","createTime":"2019-03-16T06:14:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T13:52:21.000Z","uid":89046,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"64d1d3ed5c10e914c34e8c22e7ea12b8c68bc443","tid":1063884,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T06:14:07.000Z","msg":"【李克強記者會動作金句多多】<br />\n【談改革效率：「一竿子插到底，插到市場主體」】<br />\n<br />\n有線中國組<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/2063203893824086/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F265944843550009%2Fposts%2F2063203893824086%2F&d=hEl8YzVD%2FOsYsQiwoICJnEuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=29a825cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/2063203893824086/</a><br />\n<br />\n全國人大閉幕式上，李克強的工作報告以0票反對通過，是他上任6年來的第一次。隔了一個小時後，他出現在總理記者會上，面對路透社記者質疑中國經濟變差，也顯得很有信心。縱觀全場記者會，李克強都表情動作多多，提到自己負責的經濟政策時更大派金句，語氣堅決。<br />\n<br />\n「政府就要過緊日子就要讓利，政府的存量利益也要動，得罪人也要動！」<br />\n<br />\n「要確保堅決地動存量利，割自己的肉！」<br />\n<br />\n「一竿子插到底，插到市場主體。我們4月1日要減增值稅，5月1日減社保費，到時全面推開，我看還沒有其他辦法，比這種辦法給企業帶來的感受更公平和有效。」<br />\n<br />\n與上年的記者會相比，李克強說話的手勢多了，雙手揮來揮去，幾乎沒有停過，甚至連坐都坐不定。政治學者吳強認為，李克強的刻意表現是在掩飾不安的一面。<br />\n<br />\n「這種刻意似乎是在表明他有一種不安，這種不是一個失敗者的不安，不是一個喪權者的不安，而是一個在兩會成功，特別今天政府工作報告得到零票反對下，得到一種小小的喜悅。他要控制這種喜悅，避免功高震主。」<br />\n<br />\n他更觀察到李克強特地換了領帶。「這次的記者會似乎比他幾個小時前，他在參加閉幕式的時候，他的領帶也換了一下。我注意到他記者會是帶藍色領帶，閉幕式上他是紅色的領帶，或者是對這記者會有個專門的暗示，把紅領帶換成藍色領帶，似乎是想表達一種比較低調的信號。」<br />\n<br />\n#有線中國組<br />\n#李克強<br />\n#政府工作報告<br />\n#零票反對"},{"pid":"44dae6b91cf7df11b017d4d94942c6f4d4155848","tid":1063884,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T06:51:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f7f28356b2ab1d56c081d682e1c5b27362bebc5b","tid":1063884,"uid":89046,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T11:51:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wwm6Ydj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwwm6Ydj.jpg&h=6e1cfa61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EGAGM6E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEGAGM6E.jpg&h=53fdb485&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7857d2a8837c937998a0a528810427ddbc0954fa","tid":1063884,"uid":162272,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T12:48:31.000Z","msg":"作緊詞咁 押哂韻"},{"pid":"385d0350b4ee94f3cb3b0c8a4c15c4456af92e26","tid":1063884,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7857d2a8837c937998a0a528810427ddbc0954fa","tid":1063884,"uid":162272,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T12:48:31.000Z","msg":"作緊詞咁 押哂韻"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T21:49:31.000Z","msg":"rap嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f4fcc07e0954b8fb861d58b20760df296565e24","tid":1063884,"uid":193893,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"385d0350b4ee94f3cb3b0c8a4c15c4456af92e26","tid":1063884,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7857d2a8837c937998a0a528810427ddbc0954fa","tid":1063884,"uid":162272,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T12:48:31.000Z","msg":"作緊詞咁 押哂韻"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T21:49:31.000Z","msg":"rap嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T23:02:37.000Z","msg":"一桿子 插到底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n插到市場主體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解仆直解體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蘇聯有版你睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"351cdbbedd9fc125927afedb2fd4b5daca11b252","tid":1063884,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T23:05:08.000Z","msg":"中國股市直插到底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f94b8a0802af1ab46d4dad3ce3d09a128407d96","tid":1063884,"uid":57376,"like":2,"